The owners of the house had occupied 11 of the 13 apartments in the building on the street Balmes No. 51 (Barcelona).
The 12 housekeepers left the building yesterday afternoon without any resistance.
All points to the fact that the nightmares of the neighbors of the house No 51 on the street Balmes have found an end.
Twelve people left the building, which they had been illegally occupied and in which they had organized huge festivals that had led the neighborhood to despair, on a voluntary basis yesterday afternoon.
