It has the shape of a cigar, with a diameter of one meter, is introduced into the inside of the pipe and moved through the gas pressure.
After three full days of movement by the line at a speed of 3 meters per second, the device provides the most accurate information on any deformations of the metal on its arrival.
The gas pipeline was designed to work for fifty years without even having to undergo the least repair.
The gas circulation is easily guaranteed by pressure.
